.header-secound
  .header-secound__logo
    = link_to "#" do
      = image_tag "//www-mercari-jp.akamaized.net/assets/img/common/common/logo.svg?891577966", class: 'header-secound__logo__icon'
  .header-secound__signup-bar
    %ol.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--first.red-color-text
        会員情報
        .bubble.red-color
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--secound
        電話番号認証
        .bubble
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--third
        お届け先住所入力
        .bubble
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--forth
        支払い方法
        .bubble
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--fifth
        完了
        .bubble
.main-secound
  .main-secound__block
    %h2.main-secound__block__title
      会員情報入力
  .main-secound__contents
    .main-secound__contents__container
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          ニックネーム
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"例) メルカリ嵩将", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          メールアドレス
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"PC・携帯どちらでも可", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          パスワード
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"6文字以上", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          パスワード(確認)
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"6文字以上", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %h3.main-secound__contents__container__block__title
          本人確認
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__description
          安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          お名前（全角）
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form-half
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"例）徳川", type:"text"}
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"例）家康", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          お名前カナ（全角）
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form-half
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"例）トクガワ", type:"text"}
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"例）イエヤス", type:"text"}
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          生年月日
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__require
          必須
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__form--select-box
            %select.year-js
              %option{value: ""} --
              - number = 2019
              - while number >= 1900 do
                %option{value: "#{number}"} 
                  = number
                - number -= 1
            %span.word
              年
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__form--select-box
            %select.month-js
              %option{value: ""} --
              - number = 1
              - while number <= 12 do
                %option{value: "#{number}"} 
                  = number
                - number += 1
            %span.word
              月
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__form--select-box
            %select.day-js
              %option{value: ""} --
              - number = 1
              - while number <= 31 do
                %option{value: "#{number}"} 
                  = number
                - number += 1
            %span.word
              日
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__info
          ※ 本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__white-box
          %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__text
            私はロボットではありません。
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__icon
            .main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__icon__image
            %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__icon__name
              reCAPTCHA
          .main-secound__contents__container__block__authentication__link-block
            = link_to "プライバシー", "https://www.google.com/intl/ja/policies/privacy/" ,class:'link-gray'
            %span.link-gray
              -
            = link_to "利用規約","https://www.google.com/intl/ja/policies/terms/" ,class:'link-gray'
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text-message
          「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、
          = link_to "利用規約", "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos_list/" ,class: 'link-blue'
          同意したものとします
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__btn-next
          = link_to "次へ進む" ,"signup2" ,class:'link-white'
      .main-secound__contents__container__block.text-right
        .main-secound__contents__container__block--information
          = link_to "#" ,class:'link-blue' do
            本人情報の登録について
            %i.fa.fa-chevron-right
= render partial: 'footer'


